# Build context = repo root. Keep src/, tools/, *.sln, Directory.Build.*; drop the
# rest so the context stays small and stale build output never leaks into the image.
.git
.github
**/bin
**/obj
**/.vs
**/.idea
.dev
**/.venv
**/node_modules
site
docs
tests
*.user
# NOTE: deploy/ is intentionally NOT ignored - the runtime stage copies
# deploy/compose/entrypoint-gert.sh from the build context.
